  "title": "Maintenance Engineer (Lift | LMD | IOT | ELV – Project Management)",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well established Company</strong></li><li><strong>Basic $3500 - $ 5000 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: Northeast</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: 8:30am – 5:30pm (Mon to Fri) </strong></li><li><strong>Lift Maintenance; LMD (Lift Monitoring Device); IOT; ELV </strong></li><li><strong>Training Provided </strong></li></ul><p><strong></strong></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong><br /></p><ul><li><strong>Project lead and drive project towards goal achievement</strong></li><li><strong>Maintenance of completed projects in DLP phases and/or renewed, continuation of maintenance work scope</strong></li><li>Lead tram to be productive and explore all avenues in good control and execution of project to achieve targeted costing budget</li><li><strong>Perform indoor and outdoor activities (on site) </strong></li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p> </p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Diploma and/or Degree in Electrical and Electronics Engineering or equivalent</li><li>Experience in CCTV / IoT  Project Management</li><li>Training Provided </li></ul><p></p><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>NG DIAUM YEE (R2198031)<br />EA Recruitment Pte Ltd<br />EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
